The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 IN THE CITY

 The CAB is going to present a unique slide show during Sundays annual awards ceremony at Town Hall. When the players will receive the prizes, they will get to see clippings of their last seasons performances on screen. A dress rehearsal to this effect was completed on Saturday in presence of president Prasun Mukherjee and joint secretaries Saradindu Pal and Amitava Banerjee.

 East Bengal XI will face Chirag United XI in a friendly at the East Bengal ground on Sunday. The match is a benefit tie for ex-footballer Parimal Dey. 

 GENERAL: CAB annual awards at Town Hall from 5pm.

 SWIMMING: State-level meet at the Santosh Mitra Square pool.




